{"base_path":"/","components":null,"consumes":"[\"application/json;charset=UTF-8\",\"application/json\"]","definitions":{"ErrorResponse":{"description":"请求失败时返回的错误对象。","properties":{"error_code":{"description":"**参数解释**:ModelArts错误码。\n**取值范围**:不涉及。","type":"string"},"error_msg":{"description":"**参数解释**:具体错误信息。\n**取值范围**:不涉及。","type":"string"}},"required":["error_code","error_msg"],"type":"object"},"TagRequest":{"description":"Lite Server超节点创建以及删除的标签列表。","properties":{"tags":{"description":"**参数解释**:标签列表。","items":{"$ref":"#/definitions/TmsTag"},"maxItems":20,"minItems":1,"type":"array"}},"required":["tags"],"type":"object"},"TagResponse":{"description":"Lite Server超节点查询返回标签列表。","properties":{"tags":{"description":"标签列表。","items":{"$ref":"#/definitions/TmsTag"},"maxItems":20,"minItems":0,"type":"array"}},"type":"object"},"TmsTag":{"description":"TMS的标签结构体。","example":{"key":"test","value":"service-gpu"},"properties":{"key":{"description":"**参数解释**:TMS标签的key。\n**约束限制**:长度限制为128个字符,支持任意语种字母、数字、空格,以及_ . : = + - @特殊字符,但首尾不能含有空格,不能以_sys_开头。\n**取值范围**:不涉及。\n**默认取值**:不涉及。","maxLength":128,"minLength":1,"pattern":"^((?!\\s)(?!_sys_)[\\p{L}\\p{Z}\\p{N}_.:=+\\-@]*)(?<!\\s)$","type":"string"},"value":{"description":"**参数解释**:TMS标签的value。\n**约束限制**:长度限制为255个字符,支持任意语种字母、数字、空格,以及_ . : / = + - @特殊字符。\n**取值范围**:不涉及。\n**默认取值**:不涉及。","maxLength":255,"minLength":0,"pattern":"^([\\p{L}\\p{Z}\\p{N}_.:\\/=+\\-@]*)$","type":"string"}},"required":["key","value"],"type":"object"}},"description":null,"group_id":"ade740e866904a7dbdaa5ec0f538d4d0","host":"modelarts.cn-north-4.myhuaweicloud.com","id":"19c2148583484c19805f05509fabcef3","info_version":"v1","method":"post","name":"CreateHyperinstanceTags","parameters":{},"paths":{"/v1/{project_id}/dev-servers/hyperinstance/{id}/tags/create":{"post":{"consumes":["application/json"],"description":"创建Lite Server超节点标签接口用于为Lite Server超节点添加自定义标签。该接口适用于以下场景:当用户需要对Lite Server超节点进行分类管理或标记特定信息时,可以通过此接口为指定的超节点创建标签。使用该接口的前提条件是Lite Server超节点已存在,用户具有创建标签的权限。创建操作